OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie says it is good to be
OL,4,Chome as she returns to Today show
OL,6,FSavannah Guthrie has said it is "good
OL,7,Fto be home", as she returned to the
OL,8,FToday show for the first time since
OL,9,Fher mother went missing.
OL,11,FThe broadcaster, 54, has returned to
OL,12,Fher post on the US breakfast programme
OL,13,Fmore than two months after her mother,
OL,14,FNancy Guthrie, went missing from her
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,17,FAs Guthrie kicked off the NBC news
OL,18,Fshow on Monday, she said: "Welcome to
OL,19,FToday on this Monday morning. We are
OL,20,Fso glad you started your week with us,
OL,21,Fand it's good to be home."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
