OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie says it is good to be
OL,4,Chome as she returns to Today show
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHer co-host, broadcaster Craig Melvin,
OL,12,Fsaid: "It is good to have you back
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,F"So good to have you back."
OL,17,FThey showed crowds of fans carrying
OL,18,Fsigns welcoming Guthrie back and
OL,19,Fshowing their support for her, as they
OL,20,Fgathered outside NBC's New York
OL,21,Fstudios where the show is filmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
