OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie says it is good to be
OL,4,Chome as she returns to Today show
OL,6,FGuthrie also went outside during the
OL,7,Fbroadcast and was greeted by the
OL,8,Fcheering crowd, and said: "You guys
OL,9,Fhave been so beautiful, I've received
OL,10,Fso many letters and so much kindness.
OL,12,F"To me and my whole family, we feel
OL,13,Fit, we feel your prayers. Thank you so
OL,14,Fmuch."
OL,16,FIt has been reported that her mother,
OL,17,FNancy Guthrie, 84, was last seen at
OL,18,Fabout 9.45pm near her home in Tucson,
OL,19,FArizona, on January 31, and was
OL,20,Freported missing at midday the next
OL,21,Fday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
