OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie says it is good to be
OL,4,Chome as she returns to Today show
OL,6,FShe is believed to have been taken
OL,7,Fagainst her will, and two alleged
OL,8,Fransom notes were sent to US media and
OL,9,Fincluded a deadline for a payment to
OL,10,Fbe made by February 9.
OL,12,FPolice have not been able to verify
OL,13,Fwhether the ransom notes are real.
OL,15,FGuthrie has also made multiple pleas
OL,16,Fon social media alongside her siblings
OL,17,FCamron and Annie, directed at her
OL,18,Fmothers' alleged kidnappers and
OL,19,Fbegging for her to return home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
