OL,3,CSavannah Guthrie says it is good to be
OL,4,Chome as she returns to Today show
OL,6,FGuthrie, a prominent morning TV
OL,7,Fpresenter in the US, temporarily
OL,8,Fstepped away from Today and stood down
OL,9,Ffrom NBC's coverage of the winter
OL,10,FOlympics in February.
OL,12,FGuthrie has held her role on the Today
OL,13,Fshow almost 14 years, having first
OL,14,Fappeared as a presenter in 2012.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
